WEBVTT

00:00:28.568 --> 00:00:31.158
[Soldiers don't worry!]

00:00:31.202 --> 00:00:32.680
[You'll wear uniforms!]

00:00:33.220 --> 00:00:34.890
[You'll have free cars!]

00:00:34.920 --> 00:00:35.660
[Free beans!]

00:00:35.680 --> 00:00:39.216
Many of these children
are under 15 years old,

00:00:39.240 --> 00:00:41.210
and that is a war crime.

00:00:41.270 --> 00:00:42.410
[Free!]

00:00:43.280 --> 00:00:47.040
But you don't have to go to eastern Congo
to find human rights abuses.

00:00:47.760 --> 00:00:51.536
In America, a country
with a rapidly aging population,

00:00:51.560 --> 00:00:55.936
experts estimate
that one in 10 people over 60

00:00:55.960 --> 00:00:57.960
will experience abuse.

00:00:58.640 --> 00:01:00.976
It's a hidden epidemic,